18 Development Program and Fund
19 Sec. 1. As used in this chapter, "fund" refers to the school
20 intervention and career counseling development fund established
21 by section 4 of this chapter.
22 Sec. 2. As used in this chapter, "grant" refers to a grant from
23 the fund.
24 Sec. 3. As used in this chapter, "school intervention and career
25 counseling development program" refers to a program carried out
26 under this chapter:
27 (1) for kindergarten through grade 6; and
28 (2) by a licensed school counselor.
29 Sec. 4. (a) As a result of a comprehensive study conducted by the
30 department on the role of school counselors, including the
