38 chapter, the school corporation must:
39 (1) agree to evaluate the impact and results of the school
40 corporation's program; and
41 (2) submit the school corporation's findings to the
42 department.
EH 1004—LS 6983/DI 110

54
1 (c) The department shall administer the fund.
2 (d) The fund consists of:
3 (1) gifts to the fund;
4 (2) appropriations from the general assembly;
5 (3) grants, including grants from private entities; and
6 (4) a combination of the resources described in subdivisions
7 (1), (2), and (3).
