95
1 (A) A summary regarding the:
2 (i) school corporations and schools participating in the
3 pilot program;
4 (ii) implementation of the pilot program by each local
5 board;
6 (iii) results and outcomes regarding the pilot program;
7 and
8 (iv) implementation plans submitted by the local boards
9 under section 8(b) of this chapter.
